  "text": "Finally, in PNS radiation workers, we found no positive dosage response relationships between ionizing radiation dose and mortality for any cause reported. [CITATION_1] The statement was true at the time it was made. Since the data had only been \"eyeballed\" and not subjected to proper statistical analysis for dosage-response relationships nothing had been \"found.\" However, as will be seen in the sequel, strong positive relationships for lung cancer are found by any of several statistical tests.",
